  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nIt's impossible to save changes to user's profile in some cases, e.g. when using emojis:\r\n\r\n[Kazam_screencast_00059.webm](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/20650004/195840317-eb624b70-92f4-4c0a-af7d-4f83a37d321e.webm)\r\n\r\nConsole log:\r\n\r\n```\r\nERR 2022-10-17 10:46:51.495+02:00 error setting bio                          topics=\"settings-service\" tid=1034912 file=service.nim:822 errDesription=\"\\nstatus-go error [methodName:settings_setBio, code:-32000, message:invalid bio length ]\\n\"\r\n```\r\n\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\nSettings -> Profile, copy emojis hash from profile preview to the profile description multiple time to reach input length limit\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nEmojis should be counted adequately.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nEmojis are counted as a single char, resulting with error on save.\r\n\r\n",
